query:
-- Personais que não vieram do quiz (cadastro direto)
SELECT 
  p.id,
  u.name,
  u.email,
  p.subscriptionStatus,
  p.createdAt
FROM personals p
JOIN users u ON p.userId = u.id
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1 FROM quiz_responses qr 
  WHERE LOWER(qr.leadEmail) = LOWER(u.email)
)
ORDER BY p.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 10;
